sumed performance psychologist Bill Beswick's 'Changing Your Story' and would verbatim recount tracts from it like his own personal scriptures.\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"performance psychologist Bill Beswick\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2389}, {\"ngram\": \"Your Story\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2412}, {\"ngram\": \"recount tracts\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2447}, {\"ngram\": \"his own personal scriptures\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A mental health breakdown last February and the well-publicised break-up of his relationship with the mother of his three-year-old son George, has made Peaty reassess his relationship with success.\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2688, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A mental health breakdown\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2516}, {\"ngram\": \"his relationship\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2583}, {\"ngram\": \"the mother\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2599}, {\"ngram\": \"his three-year-old son\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2625}, {\"ngram\": \"George\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2632}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2648}, {\"ngram\": \"his relationship\", \"from\": 2658, \"to\": 2674}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2687}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I want to prove that you can come back from the lowest of the lows of my whole career and you can turn it around in potentially 14 months,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 2690, \"to\": 2840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lows\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2757}, {\"ngram\": \"my whole career\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2776}, {\"ngram\": \"potentially 14 months\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a very emotional person; I use my emotion to my advantage when it is required now.\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2930, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very emotional person\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2871}, {\"ngram\": \"my emotion\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 2889}, {\"ngram\": \"my advantage\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I like to live simply.\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2955, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have just done a FaceTime with my son, and he said, 'Daddy, are you the fastest boy?'\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 3043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2975, \"end\": 2983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FaceTime\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.843457828004619e-18, \"text\": \"FaceTime\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FaceTime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FaceTime\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my son\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 2995}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest boy\", \"from\": 3026, \"to\": 3041}]}, {\"sentence\": \"and that's kind of my purpose now: to prove that I am the fastest boy for my son because he only sees it as that.\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"kind of my purpose\", \"from\": 3055, \"to\": 3073}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest boy\", \"from\": 3098, \"to\": 3113}, {\"ngram\": \"my son\", \"from\": 3118, \"to\": 3124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Getting to the starting line is a huge one for me, but I am not one of those people to give out medals for turning up.\", \"from\": 3159, \"to\": 3278, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the starting line\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3188}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge one\", \"from\": 3192, \"to\": 3202}, {\"ngram\": \"those people\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3243}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 3256, \"to\": 3262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a little bit older now, a little bit wiser, a little bit more open-eyed about what is around me, and a lot calmer.\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never been this calm and relaxed before an Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 3401, \"to\": 3461, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this calm\", \"from\": 3419, \"to\": 3428}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympics\", \"from\": 3448, \"to\": 3459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Michael Phelps is the only male swimmer to have won three straight golds in one event, a pretty exclusive club Peaty seeks to join.\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3463, \"end\": 3477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.202107872094464e-44, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only male swimmer\", \"from\": 3481, \"to\": 3502}, {\"ngram\": \"three straight golds\", \"from\": 3515, \"to\": 3535}, {\"ngram\": \"one event\", \"from\": 3539, \"to\": 3548}, {\"ngram\": \"a pretty exclusive club\", \"from\": 3550, \"to\": 3573}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 3574, \"to\": 3579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like Peaty, Phelps's struggles outside the pool have been well publicised.\", \"from\": 3596, \"to\": 3670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3608, \"end\": 3614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 4.829938289241973e-12, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3606}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 3635, \"to\": 3643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The all-time record 28 medals he won came at a cost, with feelings of depression and anxiety morphing into suicidal thoughts and substance abuse.\", \"from\": 3671, \"to\": 3816, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The all-time record 28 medals\", \"from\": 3671, \"to\": 3700}, {\"ngram\": \"a cost\", \"from\": 3716, \"to\": 3722}, {\"ngram\": \"feelings\", \"from\": 3729, \"to\": 3737}, {\"ngram\": \"depression\", \"from\": 3741, \"to\": 3751}, {\"ngram\": \"anxiety\", \"from\": 3756, \"to\": 3763}, {\"ngram\": \"suicidal thoughts\", \"from\": 3778, \"to\": 3795}, {\"ngram\": \"substance abuse\", \"from\": 3800, \"to\": 3815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Michael had a lot of things going on between all that success,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3818, \"to\": 3891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Michael\", \"from\": 3819, \"to\": 3826}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3831, \"to\": 3836}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 3840, \"to\": 3846}, {\"ngram\": \"all that success\", \"from\": 3864, \"to\": 3880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My journey feels very similar in some ways.\", \"from\": 3893, \"to\": 3937, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My journey\", \"from\": 3894, \"to\": 3904}, {\"ngram\": \"some ways\", \"from\": 3927, \"to\": 3936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have got to deal with the cards.\", \"from\": 3938, \"to\": 3974, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the cards\", \"from\": 3964, \"to\": 3973}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have questioned whether I had enough in me to go for a third Olympics, but I decided I was willing to pay that cost, and I am excited to see what I can do.\\\"\", \"from\": 3975, \"to\": 4133, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a third Olympics\", \"from\": 4030, \"to\": 4046}, {\"ngram\": \"that cost\", \"from\": 4083, \"to\": 4092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This new version of Peaty is more balanced and, perhaps, more likeable, his answers honest, considered, and intelligent.\", \"from\": 4135, \"to\": 4255, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This new version\", \"from\": 4135, \"to\": 4151}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 4155, \"to\": 4160}, {\"ngram\": \"his answers\", \"from\": 4207, \"to\": 4218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is